content.title: Go lebelela segokaganyi sa phitlhelelo
content.howToUseTooltip:
Fa tlase fano go na le diponagalo dingwe tsa go tshwaya tsa noutu eno tse di ka dirisiwang go tlhopha ditiro, tse di jaaka go tobetsa, go tlatsa sekwalwa, jj.

Boleng jwa tshwano bo ka nna jwa boelediwa mo tsebeng ya tiriswa. Fa o kopana le dipoeletso, tsweetswee apara ditlhopho tse dingwe tsa tshwano go bona gore o tlhomologile.

Lefoko le lehibidu le supa gore boleng jwa tshwano bo a boeletswa, lefoko le letala le supa gore boleng jwa tshwano bo tlhomologile mo patlong ya tsebe ya ga jaana, mme lefoko le lentsho le supa gore ga go na papiso e e boaboelediwang.
content.otherNodesSummary: Dinoutu tse dingwe mo lefelong leno
